	space above, and don't add \parskip to space above.  Suggestion
	from Han-Wen Nienhuys <hanwen@cs.uu.nl>, implementation ideas from
	Stepan Kasal <kasal@math.cas.cz>, 16 Sep 2003 11:30:43 +0200.

